dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Telegraph Peak and Phelan quadrangles, San Bernardino County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base maps from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangles TELEGRAPH PEAK AND PHELAN, CA 1988, DMA 2452 I SE - Series V895" "Prepared in cooperation with the Angeles National Forest." "Michael Woodburne honorary map." "First printing, October 2003." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, index to sources of geology, and 2 col. cross sections. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
